description:
Do you love singing karaoke with friends? Well, this video is for you! In "In the sweet by and by," we'll be covering all the lyrics to all your favorite songs!
If you're looking for a fun and easy way to practice your singing skills, this is the video for you! In this video, we'll be covering all the lyrics to all your favorite songs and having a lot of fun doing it! So join us in "In the sweet by and by," and let's have some fun singing karaoke together!

Title: In the Sweet By and By
Author: Sanford Fillmore Bennett (1868)
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters  youtube production!
Motion Graphics Used : NOYA STUDIO - THE KING OF MOTION GRAPHICS https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKJh...
